<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>أَقُولُ بِحَمْدِ اللهِ قَوْلاً مُنَقَّحًا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَلَوْ أَنَّ فَهْمِي قَاصِر فِي الْمَسَائِلِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>عَلَيْهِ مِنْ النَّصِّ الصَّرِيحِ شَوَاهِدٌ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>إِذَا قُلْتُهُ يَهْوِي لَهُ كُلَّ عَاقِلِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>أَسِرُّ بِمَا بِي وَالْعُيُونُ عَوَابِرٌ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>بِدَمْعٍ على الْخَدَّيْنِ ثَجًّا بِوَابِلِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَفِي مُدَّعِي الإِسْلامِ قَلْبِي كََأَنَّهُ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>عَلَى الْمُهْلِ مِنْهُمْ لَيْسَ عَنْهُمْ بِذَاهِلِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>فَمَا بَيْنَ دَهْرِي وَمَا بَيْنَ مُشْرِكٍ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَلَمْ يَعْرِفِ الإِسْلامَ غَيْرُ الْقَلائِلِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَلَوْ بَذَلُوا الأَمْوَالَ نَفْلاً لِرَبِّنَا<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>إِذَا الْفَرْضُ ضَاعَ لا غِنَى بِالنَّوَافِلِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>تَرَكْنَا الْكِتَابَ وَالْحَدِيثَ وَرَاءَنَا<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>لأَجْلِ مَجَلاتٍ أَتَتْ بِالتَّهَازُلِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>لَقَدْ حَصَّلَ الْمَقْصُودَ مِنَّا عَدُوَّنَا<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَمَقْصُودُنَا مِنْهُمْ فَلَيْسَ بِحَاصِلِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>مَشَيْنَا جَمِيعًا فِي فَسَادِ صَلاحِنَا<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَرُمْنَا مَرَامًا خَاسِرًا غَيْرَ طَائِلِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>وَتَسْتَعْجِبُ الأَعْدَاءُ مِنَّا لأَنَّنَا<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>كَمِثْلِ الْقَطَا تَصْطَادُنَا بِالْحَبَائِلِ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>أَحَاطَتْ بِنَا الأَعْدَاءُ مِنْ كُلِّ جَانِبٍ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>كَأَنَّا طَعَامٌ قَدَّمُوهُ لآكِلِ<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>ج<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>